<p class="title">Chapter 1</p>
<p class="para">She awoke to pain that felt like it was ripping her apart.<br>She couldn't open her eyes,  move her body, nor muster the strength to speak. It was as if she was an inanimate object.<br><i>How long have I been like this?</i><br>Slowly, her pain began to subside. As she began to look around, tears started to dribble down her face as she tried to wipe them away.<br>She noticed that the room around her was entirely barren.</p>
